from sys import stdin
from math import ceil, sin, radians

h, v = [int(i) for i in stdin.readline().split()]

print(ceil(h/sin(radians(v))))

import math

h, v = map(int, input().split())

print(math.ceil(h / math.sin(math.radians(v))))


from math import *
